description: Number of n-node unlabeled connected graphs without endpoints.
comments: Also number of n-node unlabeled connected mating graphs, cf. A006024 and A092430 (conjectured by Vladeta Jovovic, proved by G. Kilibarda). - _Vladeta Jovovic_, Oct 07 2004
references: F. Harary and E. Palmer, Graphical Enumeration, (1973), formula (8.7.11).
Goran Kilibarda, "Enumeration of unlabeled mating graphs", Belgrade, 2004, to be published.
R. W. Robinson, Numerical implementation of graph counting algorithms, AGRC Grant, Math. Dept., Univ. Newcastle, Australia, 1977.
N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
links: R. W. Robinson, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..26
David Cook II, Nested colourings of graphs, arXiv preprint arXiv:1306.0140, 2013
Goran Kilibarda, Enumeration of Unlabeled Mating Graphs, Graphs and Combinatorics, Volume 23, Number 2 / April, 2007, pp. 183-199.
Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, Connected Graph.
